OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a
OL,6,Fmostly clear start, areas of low cloud
OL,7,Fwill spread from the east through
OL,8,FWednesday night, along with a chance
OL,9,Fof mist and fog. Chilly, with an
OL,10,Fisolated frost possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSome early low cloud, mist
OL,13,Fand fog will soon clear to give
OL,14,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,15,Fsunny spells. Mild inland, but cooler
OL,16,Ftowards the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
